flowchart TD
    A[Start Application] --> B[Initialize Calendar & People]
    B --> C[Display Main Menu]

    C -->|Calendar| D[Calendar Menu]
    C -->|People| E[People Menu]
    C -->|Exit| F[End Application]

    %% Calendar options
    D -->|List Events| G[Show Events]
    D -->|Search Events| H[Search by Title or Date]
    D -->|Add Event| I[Enter Event Details]
    D -->|Modify Event| J[Update Event]
    D -->|Remove Event| K[Delete Event]
    D -->|Back| C

    %% People options
    E -->|List People| L[Show People]
    E -->|Search Person| M[Search by RUT]
    E -->|Add Person| N[Enter Person Details]
    E -->|Modify Person| O[Update Person]
    E -->|Remove Person| P[Delete Person]
    E -->|Back| C
